Urbane, cosmopolitan, highly cerebral, and stylish best describes PR expert and lobbyist Mariam Mohammed, the head honcho of Maktoub Strategic Public Relations/Publishing. All her life she has dedicated it to hard work, the reason she is currently enjoying the fruit of her labor after years of fervent hard work in the Public Relations field and real estate.   Maureen Tamuno is bereaved     Ned Nwoko remains firm     Olori Silekunola eats humble pie   The convener of Maktoub Youth forum is yet again experiencing the proverbial seventh heaven. Yes, she is super excited as she unveils and dedicates her bundle of joy, Yusura Oluyinka Mohammed Maktoub, to the glory of her creator with a house party at her palatial Abuja mansion last week. The dedication of the baby was well attended by top political dignitaries, media executives and captains of industries who attended the well-decorated parlor dedication and also shared in her pot of joy.